<Speech gate:gateId="131145" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><Parlmember gate:gateId="130143" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΩΝ</Parlmember> (<Speech gate:gateId="131481" majorType="ChairmanSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="130636" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="130479" majorType="speaker">Γεώργιος Καλαντζής</Chairman>):</SpeechStart> Επαναλαμβάνεται η διακοπείσα συνεδρίαση.
