<Speech gate:gateId="131349" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><Parlmember gate:gateId="130347" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΩΝ</Parlmember> (<Speech gate:gateId="131551" majorType="ChairmanSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="130706" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="130549" majorType="speaker">Γεώργιος Καλαντζής</Chairman>):</SpeechStart> Ορίστε, κύριε Υπουργέ, έχετε τον λόγο.</Speech></Speech>
