<Speech gate:gateId="131351" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><Parlmember gate:gateId="130349" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΩΝ</Parlmember> (<Speech gate:gateId="131552" majorType="ChairmanSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="130707" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="130550" majorType="speaker">Γεώργιος Καλαντζής</Chairman>):</SpeechStart> Αν έχετε την καλοσύνη να σηκωθείτε…</Speech></Speech>
